snippet.title: Naruto x Boruto: Ninja Voltage - iOS/Android - Infiltrate (Gamescom Announcement Trailer)
snippet.description:
NARUTO X BORUTO Ninja Voltage is a brand new Action Strategy Role Playing game coming to iOS and Android! Play solo or team up with friends to build your own forts, set traps and defeat your rivals!
